    "text_preview": "Q: How does the author approach themes of identity and self-expression?"
  },
  {
    "id": 78,
    "properties": {
      "text": "A: The idea of embracing one's authentic self and expressing individuality runs throughout the document. The author advocates \"full expression\" (point 2), letting one's \"weirdness come out\" (point 15), and rejecting conformity to a restrictive \"high school mentality\" (point 23). Unrestrained self-expression appears to be valued."
    },
