    "text_preview": "Q: What is the significance of the point about \"Maximizing Beauty\"?"
  },
  {
    "id": 80,
    "properties": {
      "text": "A: The very first point states \"maximize the beauty - fully channel the beauty with in.\" This concept of actively maximizing and channeling beauty, both inward and outward, seems to be a guiding principle or ethic for the author. It's one of the few ideas repeatedly emphasized throughout the wide-ranging ideas in the document."
    },
