    "text_preview": "Q: What is the significance of the discussion on different types of silence?"
  },
  {
    "id": 86,
    "properties": {
      "text": "A: Point 12 references Foucault's ideas about \"different types of silences\" between friends. This hints at the author's interest in the nuances of communication, intimacy, and the meaning of unspoken elements in relationships. Silence is framed as something worth examining philosophically."
    },
