    "properties": {
      "text": "A: There are several points that advocate for exploring new perspectives and experiences. Point 12 says \"Explore [nihilism]\" despite its stark worldview. Point 22 celebrates making art that pushes boundaries of what seems possible. The author seems to value an attitude of curiosity and openness to the unfamiliar."
